龙之皇冠普遍得到了很高的评价。游戏网站[[IGN|IGN]]在游戏的发售前给出了8.5/10的高分，并评价为Great<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/games/dragons-crown/ps3-110941|title=Dragon's Crown Review Hacking-and-slashing made new again|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2013-08-01|archive-date=2017-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213075405/http://www.ign.com/games/dragons-crown/ps3-110941|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同样给出Great评价的还有GameSpot.com，他们打出了8/10的评分，并提出虽然画面精良，但是人物造型有潜在的色情倾向，给游戏带来了一定程度的污点；以及剧本缺乏深度的意见<ref name=gspot />。Gametrailers.com则给出了9/10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gametrailers.com/games/i0fkpf/dragon-s-crown|title=Dragon's Crown|publisher=Gametrailers.com|accessdate=2013-08-01|archive-date=2013-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111071752/http://www.gametrailers.com/reviews/rpkq37/dragon-s-crown-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>分的评价。

另外，KOTAKU对龙之皇冠的评价为值得购买<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/dragons-crown-the-kotaku-review-977366436/|title=Dragon's Crown: The Kotaku Review|publisher=Kotaku.com|accessdate=2013-08-05|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118021330/https://kotaku.com/dragons-crown-the-kotaku-review-977366436|dead-url=no}}</ref>，Joystiq则给出了4星半/5星的评价<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/07/31/dragons-crown-review/|title=Dragon's Crown review: King of brawlers|publisher=Joystiq.com|accessdate=2013-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130804081228/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/07/31/dragons-crown-review/|archive-date=2013-08-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，Dualshockers的评价为9/10，并认为本作令一种游戏类型再度复活<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/07/31/review-dragons-crown-vanillawares-masterpiece-revives-a-genre/|title=Review: Dragon’s Crown – Vanillaware’s Masterpiece Revives a Genre|publisher=Dualshockers.com|accessdate=2013-08-07|archive-date=2016-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009021912/http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/07/31/review-dragons-crown-vanillawares-masterpiece-revives-a-genre/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，Destructoid更是打出了9.5/10的高分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/products_detail.phtml?p=Dragon's+Crown&c=news|title=Dragon's Crown had a strong opening week in Japan|publisher=Destructoid.com|accessdate=2013-08-05|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803042227/https://www.destructoid.com/products_detail.phtml?p=Dragon%27s+Crown&c=news|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

龙之皇冠在日本发售之后第一周PS3和PSV双版本实体游戏销量合计突破17万5000张，占据日本MC周销量排行榜第二和第三位，并以96分的高分占据4Gamer读者评价排行榜第一名<ref name="mc">{{cite web|url=http://www.4gamer.net/games/117/G011794/20130731062/|title=ゲームソフト週間販売ランキング＋|date=2013-07-31|publisher=4Gamer|accessdate=2013-08-01|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030021841/https://www.4gamer.net/games/117/G011794/20130731062/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而Atlus稍后也在[[twitter|twitter]]上发布了龙之皇冠的首周销量包含下载版本已经超过30万份，出货供不应求，希望没有买到也不愿等待的玩家考虑在PSN上购买下载版的消息<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/08/02/dragons-crown-sells-more-than-300000-units-in-japan-between-retail-and-download-shortages-continue/|title=Dragon’s Crown Sells More than 300,000 Units in Japan Between Retail and Download, Shortages Continue|date=2013-08-02|publisher=Dualshockers.com|accessdate=2013-08-07|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305010709/http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/08/02/dragons-crown-sells-more-than-300000-units-in-japan-between-retail-and-download-shortages-continue/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

